@startuml sequence_add_entry
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Add Pipeline Entry

actor "Job Seeker" as User
participant "build-pdf.mjs\n(Feature 02)" as Build
participant "data/pipeline.md" as Pipeline
participant "templates/states.yml" as States

User -> Build : Generate PDF for tailored resume
Build --> User : exports/<basename>.pdf

User -> Pipeline : Open pipeline.md
User -> States : Confirm valid status value\n(e.g. Applied)
States --> User : Status confirmed valid

User -> Pipeline : Append new row:\n# | Date | Company | Role | Source\n| Applied | Rate | PDF Link | Report | Notes

Pipeline --> User : Row appended
User -> Pipeline : Commit to Git

@enduml
